c: 2
v: 96
t: "Nabiyow Diggah yahuud manô fayxih Sinaamak baakeerih gibduk Raaqa marah ken geetto, Yallat agleyta haa marak baakeerih gibduk raaqa marah ken geetto, keenik Numuk teyni Alfi Sanatih gide Qumrik geyam kicniih Qaagitah usuk tama Qumri geyaamah digaalak kaa mayayxeera, Yalli usun Abba haanam yable Rabbi kinni"